## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project aims to detect fraudulent credit card transactions using machine learning techniques.  
It focuses on handling highly imbalanced data and identifying fraud cases with high accuracy and recall.

This project was completed as part of a **one-month Data Science & Machine Learning internship**.

---

## â“ Problem Statement
Credit card fraud causes major financial losses worldwide.  
The challenge is to build a model that can:
- Accurately detect fraudulent transactions  
- Handle class imbalance  
- Reduce false negatives (missed fraud cases)

