---

## ğŸ“ˆ Model Evaluation
Because the dataset is imbalanced, accuracy alone is not sufficient.  
The following metrics were used:
- Accuracy  
- Precision  
- Recall  
- F1-Score  
- Confusion Matrix  

Special emphasis was given to **Recall**, as detecting fraud cases is critical.

